text: Naša TV was a Herzegovinian/Bosnian local commercial cable television channel based in Mostar, Bosnia and Herzegovina. Television channel is launched in March 2016 and it produces in Croatian language. "Naša TV" literally means "Our TV", in Croatian. Naša TV is available via cable systems throughout the Bosnia and Herzegovina and target audience is in Herzegovina-Neretva Canton, West Herzegovina and Canton 10, Central Bosnia and Posavina Canton and part of Sarajevo Canton. == External links == * Official website of Naša TV * Naša TV in Facebook * Communications Regulatory Agency of Bosnia and Herzegovina == References == Category:Defunct television channels in Bosnia and Herzegovina Category:Television channels and stations established in 2016
